sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant Device1 as Device 1
    participant Device2 as Device 2
    participant System as System

    User->>Device1: Initiate session
    Device1->>System: Connect to system
    System-->>Device1: Acknowledge connection

    User->>Device2: Initiate session
    Device2->>System: Connect to system
    System-->>Device2: Acknowledge connection

    Device1->>System: Send data from Device 1
    System-->>Device1: Process data

    Device2->>System: Send data from Device 2
    System-->>Device2: Process data

    User->>Device1: Request data
    System-->>Device1: Return data

    User->>Device2: Request data
    System-->>Device2: Return data